      <title>有组织犯罪正在通过欧洲房地产洗钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/organized-crime-is-laundering-money-through-european-real-estate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据一份关于整个地区有组织犯罪的报告，欧盟超过三分之一最具威胁的犯罪网络正在通过房地产洗钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/organized-crime-is-laundering-money-through-european-real-estate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
