    <item>
      <title>台湾称援助已送达数百名因地震而受困的人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/taiwan-says-aid-reaching-hundreds-of-people-stranded-by-quake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾官员表示，援助正在流向台湾东部数百人，他们在1999年以来最严重的地震中仍因道路封闭和废墟而受困。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/taiwan-says-aid-reaching-hundreds-of-people-stranded-by-quake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:21:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其加入北约盟国暂停欧洲武器条约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/turkey-joins-nato-allies-in-suspending-europe-arms-treaty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其暂停了一项对欧洲常规军事装备施加限制的武器条约，加入了北约盟国的行列，在俄罗斯去年退出该协议后，土耳其也采取了同样的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/turkey-joins-nato-allies-in-suspending-europe-arms-treaty</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:11:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抗议和价格上涨推动欧洲重新制定绿色协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/protests-and-prices-push-europe-into-remaking-its-green-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2019年底，欧盟启动了绿色协议，旨在引领世界进入可持续的未来。然后是新冠疫情、通胀飙升、供应链断裂和俄罗斯入侵乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/protests-and-prices-push-europe-into-remaking-its-green-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
